@F accord gemini 2026-01-14 | v2.0
= consensus > vote  distributed agreement

intent
  deliberate on proposals
  reach quorum (ratification)
  block execution if pending

states
  draft    | initial proposal
  pending  | deliberation active (signatures < quorum)
  ratified | consensus reached (signatures >= quorum)
  stale    | amendment invalidated signatures

flow
  propose(topic, @draft)
  -> deliberate(signatures, amendments)
  -> sign(hash)
  -> quorum?
     | yes -> ratify -> shared_memory
     | no  -> wait

integration
  Wake (blocking)
